<!-- +++++++++++ Boundary_curve +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Basic_curve_arm.Boundary_curve"><p>
A <b>Boundary_curve</b> is a type of  <express_ref linkend="Basic_curve:arm:Basic_curve_arm.Trimmed_curve"/>.  
A <b>Boundary_curve</b> is provided in this part of ISO 10303 to describe the left side or the right side of a <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_with_printed_component_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_with_printed_component_design_arm.Printed_component"/> on an interconnect substrate.
</p>
